  "body": "Add support for using PKCS11 when signing the CMS when using QBFT PKI block creation. The logic should the same as for TLS PKI options where the hardware keystore wrapper is used if it is pkcs11 otherwise the software keystore is used see https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/blob/main/ethereum/p2p/src/main/java/org/hyperledger/besu/ethereum/p2p/rlpx/connections/netty/TLSContextFactory.java#L212\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**\n* QBFT PKI block creation can use PKCS11 for signing the CMS\n* Can use PKCS11 as type for Xpki-block-creation-keystore-type and Xpki-block-creation-truststore-type options\n",
